  "text": "In this study, derepressed chromosomal ampC genes and pAmpC beta-lacmtase genes were equally prevalent in E. coli. This has also been observed in a French study [CITATION_1] , but a higher prevalence of derepressed chromosomal ampC genes was detected in Belgium. [CITATION_2] This difference could result from differences in selection of isolates.",
